title: The Model X is on a crucial mission for Tesla - Foster's Daily Democrat
text:
Elon Musk's startup electric-car maker threw a very big, very Tesla party in Fremont, California, where Tesla is headquartered and operates its main factory. We already knew pretty much everything about the Model X, but seeing was definitely believing.
